    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Drive home a dependable favorite! This well-maintained vehicle is in great shape and ready for its next adventure. It offers a smooth ride and a clean interior that shows it's been cared for over the years. This is a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality car that still looks and performs wonderfully!",
      "price": 38500.0,
